</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="215" pageNumber="977" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="215.[131,1340,274,830]" pageId="215" pageNumber="977">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[132,479,707,741]" pageId="215" pageNumber="977">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. The Fraternal 
<taxonomicName authority="Kaup, 1829" box="[183,272,747,780]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="215" pageNumber="977" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Myotis</taxonomicName>
is relatively widespread, but very little is known aboutits ecology and threats.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
